1) Project Structure
2) How to install


1) Project Structure:
------------------

+ bin/				: all binaries can be found there
  + helpers/			: all php functions that are used as helpers
  + patterns/			: all php classes are in this directory
  + PhpDocumentator/		: this is the phpdocumentator that is used to generate documentation
  + tests/			: all test classes / html generated reports are there

+ documentation/		: all documentation files  
  + bouml/			: all UML reports are there (as HTML pages)
  + phpdoc/			: all generated PHP documentations 

+ assets/			: all the assets
  + css/			: css files
  + js/				: javascript files
  + img/			: images

2) How to install:
------------------
Please read the INSTALL file, or visit the demo page at <http://acoeditor.cheghamwassim.com>

